</div><p>I don't have much to say LaQuita, I just really like what you have to say and also the energy behind your post.  I feel your freedom, for lack of a better way to say it.</p><p>I am going through a stressful period, but it doesn't feel so bad.....I guess I am able to turn my attention to more positive things, away from the negative as you suggest. So much negative stuff has fallen away in my life, it's astounding, yet I find myself wanting something else.  Not sure what?  Anyway, your post speaks to that something else.....the satisfaction of self reliance perhaps?</p><p>Thanks!</p><p>Jack</p>
